Description: Papyrus fragment with a drawing of a human face on recto, and traces of 2 lines of Coptic text on verso, written against the fibres. EA 75337, 75336, 75335, 75334 are mounted together.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380760) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380760)
